<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="near-adv">near <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /nɪə(r)/    美 /nɪr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(空间、时间) 接近；靠近：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A train is <strong>coming near</strong> quickly. 
一列火车飞速驶来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The exams are <strong>drawing near</strong>. 
考试越来越近了。</p></div></div>